name: Hamilton County Health Department - Tennessee
tweet: Any drug that does not come from your pharmacy or doctor (including marijuana, cocaine, methamphetamine, and heroin) has the potential to be laced with the opioid fentanyl. Please visit our website at  https://t.co/jjE2euB2sl to learn more about the signs of an overdose.

name: Hamilton County Health Department - Tennessee
tweet: Having Narcan available can mean the difference between life or death when someone is having an opioid overdose. Recent increases in fentanyl-related overdoses have shown that now more than ever, individuals should know the signs of an overdose.  https://t.co/nG5JzvbLkU
